    {
      "instruction": "<p>Coat the <strong>aubergine pieces</strong> in the <strong>flour mixture</strong>, then press into the <strong>cheesy panko</strong> <strong>breadcrumbs</strong> firmly to evenly coat all over</p><p>Add the <strong>coated aubergine </strong>to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined tray and add a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Put the trays with the fries and the aubergine in the oven for an initial 20 min or until crispy and golden</p>",
      "order": 4,
