    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, grate your<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Combine the<strong> grated garlic</strong>,<strong> tomato paste</strong> and<strong> half </strong>your <strong>oregano</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) in a bowl with 1 1/2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[2 tbsp] </span>[2 1/2 tbsp]</span><strong> cold water</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt </strong>and<strong> sugar</strong> – this is your <strong>tomato sauce</strong></p><p>Drain your <strong>mozzarella</strong>, then pat and squeeze as much liquid out as you can with kitchen paper</p><p>Slice the <strong>drained mozzarella</strong> into 2<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>slices per person</p>",
