      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>basil</strong> as finely as you can, including the stalks</p><p>Combine the <strong>chopped basil</strong> and <strong>mayo </strong>in a bowl – this is your <strong>basil mayo</strong></p><p>Slice your <strong>brioche bun[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Wash your <strong>salad </strong>then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
