    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build your burger, add a handful of <strong>salad</strong>, then a <strong>saucy mozzarella slice</strong> to the <strong>toasted brioche base</strong>, then layer with the <strong>crispy aubergine</strong> and repeat the process</p><p>Spread the <strong>basil mayo</strong> over the<strong> toasted brioche lid </strong>and top the burger – this is your <strong>aubergine parmigiana burger</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>oregano fries </strong>and<strong> remaining salad</strong> to the side, then drizzle a little <strong>olive oil</strong> over the salad with a grind of<strong> black pepper</strong> and enjoy!</p>",
